----------------
AWS- AMPLIFY
AWS Amplify is a JavaScript library for frontend and mobile developers building cloud-enabled applications.
The fastest way to build mobile and web apps that scale
Easy to create, configure, and implement scalable mobile and web apps powered by AWS
Support iOS, Android, Web, and React Native frontends
AWS Amplify consists of a development framework and developer services
Automates the application release process of both your frontend and backend allowing you to deliver features faster

-----------------
